tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE feedback_data (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE warehouse_operations (
    operation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    operation_type VARCHAR(100),
    operation_description TEXT,
    feedback_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (feedback_id) REFERENCES customer_feedback(feedback_id)
);

CREATE TABLE feedback_analysis (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    warehouse_id INT,
    feedback_score INT,
    feedback_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES customers(customer_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (warehouse_id) REFERENCES warehouse(warehouse_id)
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  customer_id INT,
  feedback_text TEXT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE WarehouseOperations (
  operation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  operation_name VARCHAR(50),
  operation_type VARCHAR(50),
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE WarehouseEmployees (
  employee_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  employee_name VARCHAR(50),
  department VARCHAR(50),
  position VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE FeedbackAnalysis (
  analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  feedback_id INT,
  analysis_result TEXT,
  analysis_date DATE,
  analyst VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE OperationFeedbackMapping (
  mapping_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  operation_id INT,
  feedback_id INT
)
